{"commentv2": 1, "number": 9, "id": 180270, "nreplies": 1, "sticky": 0, "user": "98104", "body": "Thrall can now be involved in this fight -- Thrall was buffed to be highly resistant to the fire damage. We use him on the boss all the time (and the Tauren warriors on the Doomguards)", "date": "2007-11-06T21:15:58-06:00", "rating": 20, "indent": 0, "roles": 0, "deleted": 0, "outofdate": 0, "userRating": 0, "replies": [{"body": "One thing to keep in mind about Thrall's involvement, however, is that Azgalor performs a cleave. Keep an eye on Thrall...sometimes he can completely slip the raid's mind and prolonged periods of cleaves *can* kill him.", "creationdate": "2008-07-05T18:35:33-05:00", "id": 38684, "rating": 4, "commentid": 180270, "dataTree": 1, "roles": 0, "username": "170741", "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "downvotedByUser": false, "reportedByUser": false, "votedByUser": false}], "dataTree": 1, "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}}
