{"commentv2": 1, "number": 49, "id": 2099041, "nreplies": 2, "sticky": 0, "user": "gbalkam", "body": "Battle for Mount Hyjal Bugged?   Azgalor will not respawn after wipe / or solo death?\r\n(above inserted for search engine purposes)\r\n\r\nHere is the solution I got after opening a ticket.\r\n\r\n[i]Game Master A######s, here to help! I received your ticket on the counters for the waves being negative. I've looked over the account details in great detail to see how I can help. I thank you for your patience while waiting for a response to your ticket.\r\n\r\nThe way to fix that is to leave the instance for 30+ minutes, This means everyone in the group needs to leave for that amount of time and cannot enter during that time. With the long wait times for a response, the instance has since reset.\r\n\r\nAt this time you can easily go back and run the raid. Keep this in mind for the future. We also have Quality Assurance aware of this and looking into this.[/i]\r\n\r\nSince the raid reset today, I'll try this if it bugs on me again (aka.. I die again.. stupidity does kill!  *lol forgot to watch the bosses spells and got ganked in his rain of fire*)", "date": "2015-02-03T16:43:55-06:00", "rating": 12, "indent": 0, "roles": 0, "deleted": 0, "outofdate": 0, "userRating": 0, "replies": [{"body": "My instance glitched at 7 of 8 waves before the first boss in the Horde Encampment. The tally just stopped and all the NPCs disappeared after Thrall said we failed. Before that, they were taking about a minute to recognise when everyone had been killed. Alliance base was glitch-free though. I waited a couple of minutes for the NPCs to reappear, tried again and everything went smoothly.", "creationdate": "2016-03-21T02:42:25-05:00", "id": 935031, "rating": 1, "commentid": 2099041, "dataTree": 1, "roles": 0, "username": "Elenda", "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "downvotedByUser": false, "reportedByUser": false, "votedByUser": false}, {"body": "Here I am responding to gbalkams post exactly 2 years in the future, And Blizzard still has not fixed this bug .... ffs.", "creationdate": "2017-02-04T11:26:49-06:00", "id": 1030317, "rating": 0, "commentid": 2099041, "dataTree": 1, "roles": 0, "username": "saillaw", "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "downvotedByUser": false, "reportedByUser": false, "votedByUser": false}], "dataTree": 1, "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}}
